lyrics:
I'm a trailblazer, a trendsetter
Every move I make, it's a little bit better
I'm a genius, misunderstood by many
But I keep pushing forward, I ain't got any

I'm on a quest for greatness, nothing less
I put my heart and soul into every breath
I'm a warrior, fighting for my dreams
No matter how hard it seems

[Chorus]
Motivation, determination, that's the key
No matter what they say, I'll always believe
In myself, in my dreams, in my destiny
I'm Kanye West, and I'm living my legacy

[Outro]
So to all my dreamers out there
Keep pushing, keep striving
Believe in yourself, and you'll achieve greatness
This is Kanye West, signing off
